ation’s  independent financial advisor three times by barron’s and one of the “ most influential figures” in the investment advisory field by riabiz in  check rics background on finras brokercheck ric is the  recipient of the iarfc’s loren dunton memorial award awarded to an individual who has made a substantial contribution to the financial services profession andor the financial interests of the public he is also a member of the financial advisor hall of fame sponsored by research magazine has been named among the “ most transformative people in the industry” by investmentnews and has been voted by readers of wealth management as one of the “four most influential people in the financial services field” ric has appeared on three industry publication covers financial advisor april  the register december  and real assets adviser january  and is a recipient of ernst and young’s entrepreneur of the year award for washington dc  and the us chamber of commerce’s blue chip enterprise award  ric is a distinguished lecturer at rowan university resident expert for dr oz and former columnist for financial advisor inccom and aarp ric is also a  new york times bestselling author with more than  million copies collectively in print his nine books on personal finance have been translated into several languages and educated countless people worldwide the truth about money was recognized with an excellence in financial literacy education eifle book of the year award from the institute for financial literacy march  a gold medal axiom award march  an apex award june  and a book of the year designation by small press magazine  the lies about money was awarded the axiom personal finance book of the year march  and an eifle award october  the truth about retirement plans and iras is a  national bestseller ric rereleased his  bestseller rescue your money which has been fully revised and updated to reflect today’s economy his ninth book the truth about your future was published in march  the ric edelman show has been airing on the radio for more than  years and is heard throughout the country ric has been named among the top  talk shows hosts for four years by talkers magazine which named him the th most important radio talk show host in america in  ric’s television series and specials the truth about money airs on public television stations across the us and in asia ric publishes an awardwinning page monthly newsletter offers free online personal finance education at ricedelmancom and speaks frequently at industry conferences ric has been featured in scores of articles has interviewed on hundreds of radio stations and every major television network and has been quoted by a vast range of newspapers and magazines he has testified before congress three times has participated in an sec roundtable and was appointed by presidents bill clinton and george w bush as a delegate to all three national summits on retirement savings ric taught personal finance at georgetown university for nine years and has guest lectured at roger williams university george washington university and rowan university where he was the first to be awarded the title of distinguished lecturer he is also a state and aicpaapproved instructor for continuing professional education and is a finra arbitrator ric graduated cum laude from rowan university in  the university bestowed upon him an honorary doctorate in  in december  ric graduated from the executive program at singularity university ric is on the advisory board of rowan university’s college of communication  creative arts and in  was inducted into the rowan public relations student society hall of fame the university named both its planetarium  and fossil park  after ric and jean edelman in recognition of their financial support to the university in  ric was named to the honorable order of the kentucky colonels ric served for five years on the board of the united way of the national capital area including two years as chairman h